'''Abu Hurayra Ɛabd Rraḥman n Ṣaxr Addusi''' (s [[Tutlayt Taɛrabt|taɛrabt]]: أبو هريرة) iga aṣaḥabi ɣ [[Lislam]] d aslmad d amḥsu n [[Lquran]], islm ɣ usggwas n 77 ahijri, ddu ufus n urqqas [[Muḥmmad]] {{saw}}, d iḥsa gis lḥadit , iga yan zɣ ṣaḥaba nna yurann tanfust nɣ lqist n urqqas d [[lḥadit anabawi|lḥadit]] nns.

Abu Hurayra , llan dids kigan n imddukal d imḍfarn d imḥḍarn lḥadiṯ anabawi nna yiwḍ lbuxari uṭṭun nnsn blli nttni zrin tamraw nna yẓṛan f Abu Hurayra. Iga Abu Hurayra yan zɣ imsɣritn n [[lquran]] ɣ [[lḥijaz]], acku ɣṛan lquran dar urqqas [[muḥmmad]] {{saw}}, ifssrt f Abi Bn Kaɛb, d yumẓt fllas Ɛbdrraḥman Bn Harmz. Yumẓ Abu Hurayra lwilaya n [[lbaḥrayn]] ɣ tizi n lxalifa [[ɛumar bn lxaṭṭab|Ɛumar Bn Lxaṭṭab]],  yumẓ ula tagldit n Lmdint zɣ usggwas n 400 ahijri ar usggwas 41 ahijri.  dffir maya yumẓ [[Lmadina Lmunawara]] ar isslmad middn lḥadit anabawi d limurat n ddin nnsn, aylliɣ immut asggwas 59 ahijri (immut ɣ usggwas 678 amiladi).

